the Supreme Court to reverse the 12-year graft conviction of
Imelda, widow of former President Ferdinand Marcos.
</P>
<P>
Ramos on Sunday ordered Bello to withdraw the petition which
has drawn strong protest from many sectors.
</P>
<P>
