</P>
<P>
-- President Slobodan Miloservic of Yugoslavia agreed to
allow diplomatic observers to enter and move through the
province of Kosovo, where Serbian troops and policemen have been
attacking the rebel Kosovo Liberation Army.
</P>
<P>
