Haotian met with visiting commander-in-chief of the Finnish
National Defense Forces, General Gustav Hagglund and his party
here today.
</P>
<P>
Chi, who is also vice-chairman of the Chinese Central Military
Commission and state councillor, said that the Chinese government
highly appreciates the independent foreign policy of peace the
Finnish government has adhered to and will never forget Finland as
one of the first European countries to recognize the People's
Republic of China.
</P>
<P>
