bring relations between the two countries and their armed forces
into a new stage.
</P>
<P>
Chi also briefed the Finnish guests on China's economic
progress and the positive measures the country has adopted to ease
the impact of Asia's financial crisis, as well as the Chinese
government's stance toward the recent nuclear tests conducted by
India and Pakistan.
</P>
<P>
China hopes Asia will maintain peace and stability, and the
country is in opposition to nuclear arms race, he underlined.
</P>
