<HEADLINE> Hong Kong Stocks Close Slightly Higher </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, June 8 (Xinhua) -- Hong Kong stocks rose 17.16
points, or 0.20 percent, to close at 8,586.63 Monday.
</P>
<P>
The market's turnover amounted to 4.548 billion HK dollars
(583.08 million U.S. dollars), 1.070 billion HK dollars (137.18
million U.S. dollars) more than that of last Friday.
</P>
<P>
The key Hang Seng Index rose 53.59 points, or 0.63 percent, to
open at 8,623.06 in the morning.
</P>
<P>
It went up 11.84 points, or 0.14 percent, to close at 8,581.31
at midday.
</P>
<P>
The Hong Kong share prices gained 11.04 points, or 0.13
percent, to close at 8,569.47 last Friday. 
</P>
