</P>
<P>
-- A secret committee headed by Education Minister
Director-General Benzion Dell recommended that the education
minister activate Jewish education programs in Arab schools in
East Jerusalem. The committee said the students there are
currently taught Palestinian National Authority curriculum in
violation of the Oslo Accords. Ministry officials said the
implementation of the proposal would lead to violence in the
area. 
</P>
</TEXT>
